# COOP/COEP so the page is cross-origin isolated — required for the
# SharedArrayBuffer-backed wasm rayon thread pool. Honored by header-capable
# static hosts (Cloudflare Pages, Netlify). For hosts that cannot set headers
# (e.g. GitHub Pages) ship a coi-serviceworker shim instead. Vite copies this
# file (public/) to the dist root.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
